
    Cloning the Repository

To clone the project, use the following command:
    git clone <repository_url>


Setting Up the Database:
    1. Create a MySQL database named easystartups.
    2. Create the following tables with their respective columns:


    Table: signup
        -> sno  (primary key (int 11))
        -> name  (Unique, (varchar 30))
        -> email (varchar 50)
        -> phone (varchar 15)
        -> password (varchar 255)
        -> datetime (current)



    Table: contact
        -> sno  (primary key (int 11))
        -> loggedinID  (int 11)
        -> name  (varchar 50)
        -> phone  (varchar 15)
        -> email  (varchar 50)
        -> city  (varchar 30)
        -> country  (varchar 30)
        -> address  (Text)
        -> skills  (Text)
        -> ideatitle  (varchar 100)
        -> ideadesc  (Text)
        -> resources  (Text)
        -> datetime (current)